Package toystore.parser

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ParserCSV
    Includes 2 public methods for writing and reading to/from a csv file, storing the csv as a List of lists of String objects.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FieldsOfInterest
    Enumeration of all fields that we need to keep from the sample csv given as input.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CsvReadingException
    Unchecked exception used to generify csv reading exceptions, in the ParserCSV class
    CsvWritingException
    Unchecked exception used to generify csv writing exceptions, in the ParserCSV class
